---
title: Coconut Shrimp & Hoisin Chicken Platter with Dark Meat Chicken, Veggie Spring Rolls, Slaw & Spicy Mango Chutney
description: This festive spread turns any night into a celebration. You'll serve crisp veggie spring rolls alongside hoisin-pineapple chicken, crunchy coconut shrimp, pineapple coleslaw with spicy mayo, and mango chutney. Layer everything in lettuce leaves to create your perfect bite, and dig into this colorful meal exactly the way you like!
